        "desc": "   Good friend,\n   At great expense to myself I have sent you this warning. Trilless the\nNorthern Sorceress defends herself with strong creatures of the deep and\nraging waters. Once you enter her river, it will sweep you forth with no\nrespite.\n   I strongly advise against taking the Northern Sorceress's river without\nproper preparations. She is well defended, and if underprepared you will\nsurely perish.\n   -Shadimar",
        "keywords": [
          "inscription"
        ]
      }
